                           <ab type="conservation">This bright brown scrap of papyrus has the left and top margins; broken off at the right, which seems to be broken as a result of a vertical fold, and lower sides. The preserved text is incomplete but clear. It has a big lacuna at the middle and badly damaged at the bottom; some fibers are frayed at the beginning of the first line.</ab>
